title: 820-00840 no 20v one port
message:
This arrived with minor liquid damage on both usb-c ports with U3200 stuck at 5v and U3100 goes to 20V and boots the board.

1.1 LDO was missing from U3200 so replaced U3200. 1.1 LDO is now restored on U3200 but still stuck at 5v. Also replaced Q3200 but no change. Fuse is good

Redriver chip on other side that doesn't show on board view or schematic looks good.

What to check next?
